        "title": "Get default terminal application on linux system using Java",
        "body": "<p>I am looking for a way to find out which one of these <code>xterm, konsole, aterm, gnome-terminal<\/code> terminal applications are present on Linux distro or a default one at runtime within a java program.<\/p>\n\n<p>It is required to execute certain commands from my java program and so need to know which terminal to use or at least if it is present and can be used.<\/p>\n\n<p>xterm can be used by default but would be good to know if there is something more advanced available to use. Even there is no guarantee if xterm is installed either.<\/p>\n",
